\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6691798\charrsid3812201 ed out who we used to go to where we'd get something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11620878 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6691798\charrsid3812201 You had an egg that day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2691140 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6691798\charrsid3812201 
We always got hot cross bun at Kenyon - Kenyon Hall. Belonged to Lord Kenyon you know. Aye. But he didn't live there, he only come three days a year but it's p
ulled down now. Pulled down now. Aye, we used to get that. Aye, that - oh we found plenty that way, we had - we had a bean}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8008749\charrsid3812201  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6691798\charrsid3812201 
feast as you say.
