d her son and I were pal of her son and I could go with 'em. Well I know this, and I never forget it, I had a hole in me pants when I}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3812201  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8008749\charrsid3812201 come}{
