 I were older than him but I never used say nothing. But it should - it should have been reversed but I never bothered, he lived so - he lived in his own - not in his own house, but a three room up and three room down lived with his son and get his own fo
od ready, done his own washing to his liking, his own cleaning and bob's your uncle.
