\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2691140 JB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6691798\charrsid3812201 Well aye, he knowed hi
s job, he knowed his job. He run two pits. He run one lower down and that - as manager, they didn't go down so often. They might have gone down once a week. The under manager went down every day and then these firemen as they had, they done three parts of
 the work because they were examining and anything wrong it's reported in book and follow on doing it, right you see.
